Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Ending
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.36,0:00:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You cowards.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.51,0:00:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Just shut up and let me shoulder it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.31,0:00:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't need to be educated by words.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.62,0:00:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You need training.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.10,0:00:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I've made my decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.88,0:00:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Eren was put under the care of the Recon Corps.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.03,0:00:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,He was to dedicate himself to missions outside the Wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.76,0:02:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,The former Recon Corps headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.96,0:02:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing more than a renovated old castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.19,0:02:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,While it definitely looks impressive,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.49,0:02:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,it's so far from the Walls and all rivers
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.02,0:02:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,that it's completely useless to the Recon Corps.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.94,0:02:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The story goes back to the ambitious early days when the Corps was formed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.56,0:02:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Who would've thought we'd end up using it again to serve as your hideout?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.58,0:03:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get cocky, new blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.79,0:03:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.98,0:03:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know the deal with this crap about you being a Titan,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.35,0:03:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,but we can't have Captain Levi babysit—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.66,0:03:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what you get for talking while riding your horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.15,0:03:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The first moments leave the most important impression.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.02,0:03:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,That newbie{same word as new blood earlier} was scared shitless.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.41,0:03:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I think he was just stunned silent by how lame you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.02,0:03:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, it's all going according to plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.98,0:03:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, you never used to talk like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.32,0:03:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,If, by chance, you're trying to imitate Captain Levi,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.93,0:03:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,you should really stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.94,0:03:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You two are nothing alike, but still...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.31,0:03:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to chain me down, Petra?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.14,0:03:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You're still ways to go to be fitting for my wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.53,0:03:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,If only you'd bled to death from biting your tongue.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.56,0:04:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You keep on boasting about how many Titans you've killed too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.46,0:04:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,So what? I've boasted about you guys too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.36,0:04:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Those people are the Recon Corps' Special Ops Squad,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.94,0:04:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}commonly known as the Levi Unit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.38,0:04:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You're pathetic!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.10,0:04:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Petra Ral. Took down 10 Titans. Assisted with taking down another 46.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.60,0:04:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Auruo Bossard. Took down 39. Assisted with another 9.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.02,0:04:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They are the elite of the elite.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.48,0:04:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Erd Gin. Took down 14. Assisted with another 32.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.77,0:04:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Günther Schultz. Took down 7. Assisted with another 40.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.69,0:04:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They are the top tier of the Recon Corps, hand-picked by Captain Levi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.56,0:04:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I went berserk, these people would be the ones to kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.23,0:04:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's covered in weeds.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.49,0:05:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.38,0:05:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been disused for a very long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.86,0:05:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Inside, a sea of dust is probably awaiting us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.02,0:05:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That is indeed a severe problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.76,0:05:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,We must sort it out immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.85,0:05:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We're done cleaning the upper floors.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.79,0:05:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Where will I get to sleep in the building, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.06,0:05:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Your room is in the basement.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.46,0:05:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The basement again, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.90,0:05:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course. You're not in complete control of yourself yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.96,0:05:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,If you drifted off and turned into a Titan,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.08,0:05:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,at least if you're underground we can restrain you right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.75,0:05:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That was one of the conditions agreed upon for us to get custody of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.62,0:05:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a rule that we must follow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.83,0:05:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take a look around the rooms.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.52,0:05:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You do this room, Eren.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.85,0:05:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.65,0:06:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got quite a despairing look on your face, Eren.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.66,0:06:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.84,0:06:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I'll be calling you Eren.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.29,0:06:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain Levi does the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.44,0:06:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, his word is the law.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.84,0:06:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Right... I don't mind that,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.95,0:06:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,but did I really have a despairing look on my face?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.89,0:06:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not surprising at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.00,0:06:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,He doesn't come across as the perfect, \Ninvulnerable hero people think he is, does he?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.36,0:06:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The true Levi is surprisingly short,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.91,0:06:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,irritable, violent, and hard to approach.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.23,0:06:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not it. I was surprised how obediently he accepts the decisions of the higher-ups.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.06,0:06:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you think that, as strong as he is, he wouldn't care about rank or the chain of command?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.98,0:06:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.46,0:06:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I expected him not to acquiesce to anyone's words.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.99,0:06:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know the details myself, but I heard he was pretty much like that originally.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.39,0:07:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Before joining the Recon Corps, he was a famous thug in the capital's underworld.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.86,0:07:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,But then, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.27,0:07:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know exactly what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.14,0:07:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,He was taken in to the Recon Corps under Commander Erwin's hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.21,0:07:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The Commander?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.03,0:07:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Eren!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.53,0:07:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.57,0:07:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no good at all. Redo it all from scratch.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.63,0:07:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,So, in thirty days, we're to go outside the Walls to build a stronghold for the supply chain?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.54,0:07:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Not to mention we'll be taking fresh graduates with us too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.12,0:07:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,If we even get any new recruits that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.76,0:07:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,In my opinion, this is far too hasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.58,0:07:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Eren's current position is a temporary thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.36,0:07:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,We must quickly and smoothly prove his usefulness to Central.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.75,0:07:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise, sooner or later, the Police will make another move to—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.68,0:08:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you take that mask off at least for me, Erwin?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.17,0:08:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You're really good at sniffing out things like this, Mike.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.29,0:08:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Too bad you have no scent whatsoever.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.31,0:08:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you when the time is right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.98,0:08:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll probably be ordered to stand by for a few more days,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.10,0:08:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,but I heard we're supposed to be going on a large-scale extramural expedition.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.44,0:08:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,And we'll be taking the new graduates with us as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.69,0:08:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this true, Erd?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.88,0:08:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it awfully soon?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.00,0:08:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Even considering that they handled this last Titan attack quite well...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.28,0:08:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard those kids' pants required multiple washings to remove the shitstains.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.72,0:08:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this all true, Captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.12,0:08:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not involved in making our plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.79,0:09:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Erwin. He's likely considering far more variables that might occur to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.63,0:09:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true that we're in an unprecedented situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.02,0:09:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,On the one hand, we lost the Maria reconquest route that we established through huge sacrifices,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.27,0:09:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,but on the other hand, we got an unexpected ray of hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.90,0:09:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I still have trouble believing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.59,0:09:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You can "turn into a Titan", but what's that mean, Eren?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.20,0:09:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,My memories from that time are quite hazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.01,0:09:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It felt like a selfless, dreaming state.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.52,0:09:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It can be triggered by hurting myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.91,0:09:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Like, if I bite—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.62,0:09:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wait, how do I know this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.32,0:09:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys know all of this too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.59,0:09:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,We couldn't get any more out of him than what's written in the reports.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.45,0:09:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,She won't stay put though.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.98,0:10:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Her meddling could even kill you, Eren.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.81,0:10:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,She? Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.37,0:10:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Good evening, gentlemen of the Levi Unit!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.31,0:10:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you made yourselves at home in the castle?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.96,0:10:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You're early.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.30,0:10:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,How could I stay put now?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.58,0:10:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Major Hanji?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.66,0:10:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for the wait, Eren.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.34,0:10:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm charged with experimenting on the two Titans we caught alive in the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.04,0:10:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to help me out with tomorrow's experiments.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.10,0:10:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I came to ask permission for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.31,0:10:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,An experiment?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.05,0:10:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What am I supposed to—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.18,0:10:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What else but that totally awesome thing you do!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.07,0:10:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... I can't give you permission myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.92,0:10:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have authority over myself, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.11,0:10:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Levi, what are Eren's plans for tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.00,0:10:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Cleaning the garden.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.29,0:10:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay then, it's decided!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.72,0:11:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be counting on you tomorrow, Eren!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.01,0:11:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.66,0:11:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,But what exactly are these experiments on the Titans?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.05,0:11:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.87,0:11:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... What exactly are these experiments...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.17,0:11:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop that. Don't ask her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.23,0:11:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.13,0:11:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You just had this expression like you wanted to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.45,0:11:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you {\i1}that{\i0}  interested?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.94,0:11:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I've got no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.11,0:11:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I've gotta tell you
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.32,0:11:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,what I know about those pretties we caught earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.13,0:12:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,First, we repeated the experiments we'd done each of the five prior times we had Titans to play with.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.17,0:12:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.16,0:12:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,First, we attempted communication.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.10,0:12:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,How are you feeling? What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.29,0:12:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Does it hurt anywhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.22,0:12:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Major, you're too close!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.78,0:12:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.61,0:12:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't the weather wonderful today?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.06,0:12:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you hungry?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.00,0:12:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.10,0:12:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa-whoa, that was close!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.95,0:12:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Major, it's too dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.00,0:12:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Sadly, communication proved impossible this time as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.30,0:12:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But for me, interacting with the Titans was so enlightening
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.84,0:12:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,that it made me entirely forget my everyday fatigue.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.99,0:12:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,A long, long time ago, there was a tribe who ate people.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.39,0:13:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,They weren't Titans like you. They were humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.26,0:13:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,They hid out in caves in the mountains,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.95,0:13:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,attacked travelers who happened to tread the roads nearby,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.96,0:13:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,robbed them of their valuables,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.04,0:13:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,killed them,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.26,0:13:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and ate their flesh.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.89,0:13:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,She's started another one of her naming ceremonies.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.54,0:13:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What did we end up with last time?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.22,0:13:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Chicacchironi and Albert.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.18,0:13:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,They kept up their resistance for 25 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.96,0:13:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,During that time, over 500 people became their prey.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.23,0:13:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That might be more than the humans you guys ate.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.90,0:13:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,They also experimented with various ways of preparing their meals.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.33,0:13:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Turning the buttocks into steaks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.00,0:13:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Cutting the thighs up into cubes and cooking a stew with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.39,0:13:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,They minced, kneaded, and fried the hard meat.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.19,0:13:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of fat and innards, they even made sausages.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.96,0:13:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. They knew the concept of "cooking".
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.22,0:14:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how they were different from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.39,0:14:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,But then those cannibals made a mistake, and they were all caught and executed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.12,0:14:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the same as you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.87,0:14:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You made the mistake of attacking mankind,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.56,0:14:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,and you were caught.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.99,0:14:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'll name you after the man who led that clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.45,0:14:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You're Sawney.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.33,0:14:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You're Bean.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.54,0:14:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,But don't worry. I won't have you executed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.20,0:14:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you, Sawney.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.11,0:14:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You too, Bean.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.74,0:14:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's try to get along.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.07,0:14:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Thus I named the 7 meter class Bean, and the 4 meter class Sawney.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.45,0:14:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Next we tried denying them sunlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.34,0:15:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The Titans are clearly less active during the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.66,0:15:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,These experiments tried to prove that they gain some kind of power from the sunlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.49,0:15:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a huge variation between individual Titans.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.77,0:15:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You've worked hard, Sawney.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.38,0:15:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Good night. See you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.74,0:15:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Sawney's activity dropped an hour after we denied them sunlight. In contrast...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.28,0:15:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You really like to stay up late, huh, Bean?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.49,0:15:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay. I'll stay here with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.99,0:15:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Bean stayed lively for three hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.20,0:15:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,They always manage to surprise me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.72,0:15:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't need water or food.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.39,0:15:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,They have vocal organs, yet they don't need to breathe.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.02,0:15:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,All they need to stay alive is sunlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.88,0:15:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}To be honest, I'm curious what would happen if we denied them sunlight completely,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.74,0:15:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}but they're such valuable experimental subjects, I can't risk them dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.60,0:16:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}We killed the previous captures by accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.20,0:16:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I accidentally hit the nape of the neck when we tried cutting their heads off.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.66,0:16:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Their names were Chicacchironi and Albert.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.02,0:16:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}They had such beautiful smiles.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.92,0:16:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I feel bad about what I did to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.28,0:16:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I don't want that to happen again... I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.38,0:16:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Major Hanji...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.58,0:16:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,And then,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.95,0:16:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I moved on to the next stage, testing their sense of pain by actually touching them!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.64,0:16:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Major, you shouldn't be the one screaming...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.24,0:16:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,How could I not scream, doing this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.52,0:16:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Bean is in so much pain!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.04,0:16:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't give up, Bean! Hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.57,0:17:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,We had to confirm whether they had any \Nweaknesses besides the nape of the neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.87,0:17:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It was really tough work.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.21,0:17:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Sawney? I just pierced your heart. Doesn't it hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.48,0:17:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,How does it feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.72,0:17:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Compared to Bean, Sawney was a lot quieter.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.46,0:17:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,He hardly reacted at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.91,0:17:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.99,0:17:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Major, fall back!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.08,0:17:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Haha, that was really close!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.07,0:17:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You're gonna end up actually dying!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.20,0:17:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Sawney isn't very good at expressing himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.78,0:17:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,He just keeps trying to bite my head off.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.31,0:17:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, Major Hanji...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.46,0:17:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you stay so carefree in front of the Titans?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.72,0:18:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,They're our natural enemies, who drove us to the brink of extinction.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.21,0:18:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you've had to face their threat a number of times before yourself too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.03,0:18:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.50,0:18:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had countless comrades murdered by them right in front of my eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.83,0:18:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Back when I joined the Recon Corps, I fought them, fueled by hate.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.92,0:18:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,But then one day I realized...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.34,0:18:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It was when I cut off and kicked the head of a 3-meter class.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.78,0:18:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It was light. Unnaturally so.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.96,0:18:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Their bodies are light.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.61,0:18:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Normally such huge bodies shouldn't even be able to stand and walk on two legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.00,0:18:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the same with every Titan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.44,0:18:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Their cut-off body parts were much lighter than they should have been for their size.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.16,0:19:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard that when you turned into a Titan, that body appeared out of thin air.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.34,0:19:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I considered that maybe the things we see are not the things that are actually there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.63,0:19:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I tried fighting the Titans out of hatred for decades.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.04,0:19:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I want to try looking at them from a \Ndifferent point of view than everyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.99,0:19:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It might prove to be futile.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.96,0:19:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But still,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.71,0:19:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.62,0:19:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Since I entered the Recon Corps, all I get are surprises.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.14,0:19:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's not just Major Hanji.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.17,0:19:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They're all weirdos.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.20,0:19:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's like a haven for freaks.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.80,0:19:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But it's also a group of people who demand change.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.56,0:20:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That is the Recon Corps.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.92,0:20:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Major Hanji,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.05,0:20:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,would you be so kind as to tell me more about your experiments?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.55,0:20:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.28,0:20:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I think it might prove useful in tomorrow's experiments if I learn as much as I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.11,0:20:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Right... I did skip over some of the details in my summary earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.56,0:20:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me tell you everything then.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.31,0:20:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It may end up taking quite a while though.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.45,0:20:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.32,0:20:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,When we first captured a Titan, I made a hypothesis.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.30,0:20:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,So you've learned nothing new from what I told you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.66,0:20:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You should have learned all this as a Cadet. You knew it all, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.99,0:20:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. There was nothing new.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.86,0:20:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,So let's go over it again, and this time I'll add my personal opinions and assumptions!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.24,0:20:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, I think we—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.38,0:20:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,First of all, the Tita—
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.19,0:21:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Is Major Hanji here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.75,0:21:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The experiment subjects...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.40,0:21:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Both of the Titans were killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.59,0:21:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Sawney! Bean!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.45,0:21:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,This can't be for real!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.20,0:21:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone tell me I'm dreaming!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.20,0:21:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Those experimental subjects were very valuable. Was it a soldier?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.99,0:21:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. The culprits are still unknown.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.29,0:21:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Both Titans were killed before sunrise.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.20,0:21:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,When a guard spotted them, they escaped using their 3D Maneuver Gear.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.38,0:21:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,So it was a premeditated move by at least two people?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.90,0:21:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Sawney!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.70,0:21:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Check it out! Major Hanji is losing her shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.44,0:21:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What on Earth...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.02,0:21:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go. This is the jurisdiction of the Police.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.04,0:21:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.83,0:22:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you see there?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.43,0:22:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Who do you think is the enemy?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.04,0:22:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.87,0:22:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, don't mind me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.03,0:24:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The investigation into the murder of Sawney and Bean is ongoing.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.52,0:24:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Mikasa, Armin, and the rest of the 104th Cadets
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.94,0:24:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,face their own fears and doubts as they choose which force they will join.
