Dialogue: 5,0:22:45.80,0:22:51.12,Ending,,0,0,0,,{\be1}If we suppose that I am not me,
Dialogue: 5,0:22:51.12,0:22:56.13,Ending,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Can you say with certainty that you are you?
Dialogue: 5,0:22:56.13,0:23:01.66,Ending,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Will you be able to pick up after yourself
Dialogue: 5,0:23:01.66,0:23:06.81,Ending,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Once your sand-like shell breaks and your heart crumbles?
Dialogue: 5,0:23:06.81,0:23:12.02,Ending,,0,0,0,,{\be1}I could hear someone calling
Dialogue: 5,0:23:12.02,0:23:15.92,Ending,,0,0,0,,{\be1}But now my ears are just ringing
Dialogue: 5,0:23:15.92,0:23:21.08,Ending,,0,0,0,,{\be1}It's as if time has frozen
Dialogue: 5,0:23:21.08,0:23:23.99,Ending,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Now, wake up
Dialogue: 5,0:23:23.99,0:23:28.96,Ending,,0,0,0,,{\be1}I began to walk through a deep dark abyss
Dialogue: 5,0:23:28.96,0:23:34.26,Ending,,0,0,0,,{\be1}As swift as a gale, I escaped for my life
Dialogue: 5,0:23:34.26,0:23:38.83,Ending,,0,0,0,,{\be1}I felt like a living corpse
Dialogue: 5,0:23:38.83,0:23:43.96,Ending,,0,0,25,,{\be1}We break out of our walls
Dialogue: 5,0:23:43.96,0:23:50.35,Ending,,0,40,20,,{\be1\an2}To reunite in worlds we've yet to map
